data.title: Bangville Police Mabel Normand, Fred Mace, Nick Cogley 1913
data.meta_description: At a farm near Bangville, the young daughter see strangers in the barn. She quickly rushes to the house and calls the police. The police engage in a haphazard rush across the countryside to get there in time.
